Each column in ORDER BY clause can have its own sort order, ascending or descending
QUERRY:
Select ID, ENAME, DOJ, SALARY, DEPT, DESIGNATION FROM Employee ORDER BY DEPT ASC, DESIGNATION DESC

5 row(s) selected
ID	ENAME	DOJ	SALARY	DEPT	DESIGNATION
4	Jack Abraham	01-Jul-14	30000	ETA	SSE
3	Emily Rayner	01-Jan-14	25000	ETA	SE
2	Ethan McCarty	01-Feb-14	90000	ETA	PM
5	Ayaz Mohammad	01-Apr-14	40000	ICP	TA
1	James Potter	01-Jun-14	75000	ICP	PM
Dept is sorted in ascending order, within the dept designation is sorted in descending order.
